I had no idea how that would go.
Conferences by three professionals in the field, how to dress problematic characters and, in addition, a seminar on how it works in the world of entertainment.
And it will be worse.
The closer the final exams are, the more information and practical tasks await us
And although the course takes place every Saturday and Sunday, there is no longer a pin.
We have once studied with the director, Alena, (in the course there is no man) how to dress the woman who does not have a perfect symmetry.
And so is the vast majority.
Someone is short-sighted, someone has a stylized figure without the proper curves, and someone is overweight.
The stylist must know how to optically soften wide shoulders, lengthen a neck or recreate the necessary curves
They have given us certain tricks on how to make the body of women of the type of Jennifer Lopez stand out, with huge breasts and hips but narrow waist and at the same time not dress her in a too challenging way
If, for example, the difference between the waist and the hips is so much that the skirt or pants do not fit, it is worth having at least an extra piece of fabric sewn to measure.
They certainly won’t regret it, because the clothes you feel perfectly are priceless.
With a tailored skirt you will feel much better than with one that does not stop moving, get up, dance at the waist, etc.
The stylized body can be allowed to wear clothes with folds, ornaments, embroidery or draping.
There are certainly many different types of information and bodies, so I am happy that I have the whole week to put all this information in my head.
And even so, I fear that with the task assigned, I already have more than enough.
Each participant in the course has been assigned two celebrities, who will have to design two changing rooms: one for the day and one for the night.
It is necessary to take into account the current appearance, the fashion style that suits the person in question.
I got to "dress" Miranda Kerr, maybe you know her from the Victoria's Secret campaign.
I scream inside, for me it is much better than, for example, Britney Spears or Christina Aguilera, who lately will have gained a hundred kilos (please take into account the exaggeration), or the very young Selena Gomez.
The dresses we have to cut them from magazines or look for them on the internet and print them, and then elaborate them graphically.
The moodboard, which is what the complete result is called, also expresses our personal style and our relationship with graphic design.
It is also important to think about the graphic part of the styling.
The stylist, therefore, does not only dress physically, but also deals, for example, with product pages in magazines (of specific topics, such as trends, bags, coats, etc.).
The stylist and designer Mario Kamen<0xC3><0xAD>k told us about it.
But all that is left for Sunday.
The stylist must have a global vision.
The three invited specialists animated the conference on Saturday with information on all types of bodies.
Stylist Honza Pokorn<0xC3><0xBD>, fashion designer Jakub Polanka and fashion photographer Ben Ren<0xC4><0x8D>.
Jakub reminded us that fashion is an illusion and the stylist should know how to take advantage of this.
And a good stylist knows how to work with the same garment in different ways.
The variability is, in this case, fundamental.
Thus, the trench coat can be dressed to the classic with jeans and t-shirt, but it also serves to dress the naked body with high heels and photograph it as if it were actually a dress.
Or simply roll it up and raise your neck to get a totally different image.
“Play with it,” he insisted.
What I value most is the following advice: "To start working, you need to know all the rules first."
"Then you can break them," Jakub said.
At last it is clear to me why we memorize all these formulas, what is combined with what, why, if it turns out that in fashion magazines we find different results.
Not to mention the parades.
Thanks to photographer Ben, I know that a stylist has to have more types of clothing in reserve than he intends to photograph.
So, for a fashion story that has ten pages (therefore, ten outfits), you have to have prepared, ready to use, at least fifteen.
And in addition to the photos the clothes work in combination with other clothes, all of them different from those used in reality.
All this must be taken into account when designing the outfit.
Honza Pokorn<0xC3><0xBD> assured us that image and style alone are, in many cases, half the success.
Just look at Madonna, who is not exactly an extraordinary singer, but the image and the marketing have made her a world star.
In the Czech Republic, at the moment, there is not yet a clear tendency to use the services of stylists.
Even famous people find it useless (my skills are enough, my physical appearance is not so important).
And when someone asks us for our services, we must bear in mind that it is very likely that they will indicate a size very different from their actual (smaller) size.
Then it remains only to gugle and find out if the magazines of the heart have already written on the subject, if a certain celebrity has fattened / thinned, etc.
On Sunday, Honza and Mario insisted that the stylist is not enough to orient himself in fashion, but has to understand the outfit.
During your work, you should especially communicate with the people you saw, so it is essential to be a good psychologist.
He knows how to value people, he doesn’t miss them, he defends their opinions.
"When a director hires you to classify her wardrobe and complete it with nice clothes, you can't take and throw away everything that was there and say, 'There's so much horror.'"
“Find at least a couple of things that you can weigh and recommend for someone to wear,” says Mario.
He himself also showed us that everything should fit in the so-called "placovka", that is, the work bag.
This is fixed around the waist and you have all the necessary tools there.
They are objects such as scissors, hair removers, or must-haves. There is also nylon thread (which serves the stylist during the photo shoot of products such as bags or hats), special clothes hook tweezers on the front, if this was older (pins and other types of hooks are not allowed, as they could damage the fabric), or a sewing set.
In order not to stay in passive listening and put something into practice, we have learned to cover the soles of the shoes.
Even during photo shoots in the studio, on a flat surface, you could damage the sole and much more the outside.
And we did nothing but coat and coat.
We could not touch the shoes with the scissors so as not to damage them by accident.
So you had to be very skilled.
Mario has given me a joy in praising my work unreservedly.
The truth is, I'm not very good at those skills.
This is just a small part of everything we have heard throughout the weekend, in the second part of the course.
I have already realized that dedicating myself to styling at a professional level is not a rosy road, but I do not care exactly what people say.
Need for Speed: The Run is set in America.
Review
A trip, in principle carefree, is complicated by a series of oversights improper of a routine trip during the morning shift.
To some extent it was possible to meet expectations, but this is of no use, if, in fact, it was not intended to do anything extraordinary.
The new installment, to which the title is added The Run, raised great expectations already before its premiere.
He promised that he would give new airs to the old racing saga Need for Speed and, in the wake of what is shown, it appears as a game that should not end up being again an action genre without more.
We were also curious to know what the inserted scenes would look like, where the main character gets out of the car and walks on his own foot.
As is often the case in the NFS series, the results do not vary much from what we expected.
There are races that can be considered acceptable, but in the total count points are lost because of absurd failures, which have already been appearing in the series for years.
In reality they cannot even be called errors, but rather it is the incomprehensible reluctance of the programmers.
The adventure begins very well.
It introduces you to a story, whose protagonist, Jack, has certain personal problems; to solve them, he is offered to participate in an illegal race throughout America.
You sit behind the wheel on the west coast, in San Francisco, and your mission is to get to New York first.
The idea is to offer something interesting.
The route is divided into ten stages and then into more than fifty races.
It follows that each race takes place by a different route and the stages are located in different environments, which are quite diverse and interesting.
Thus, one does not even remotely have the feeling that the game always offers the same thing.
Some of the environments are even pleasing to the eye, although the technical level of the graphic is equivalent to that of previous installments of the series.
Therefore, it is nothing of the other world.
But the walk through the desert, the autumn landscape or the high snow-capped mountains produce a very pleasant visual effect.
In addition, the races are diversified from time to time by an atypical element.
Thus, for example, in the desert you find a sandstorm that diminishes visibility.
On the other hand, in the mountains you have to be careful not to bury an avalanche.
According to that, each of the races is very well developed.
There are only a couple of models, but that’s enough.
For a moment, you try to overtake a required number of rivals (normal in a classic race), then you try to gain time (timed classic duel) and then a duel awaits you against a single opponent.
In the middle of all this sometimes appears the police, which only makes things even more difficult.
The novelty is the landscapes outside the car.
Interactive animations are presented when Jack, in most cases, has to escape from someone and you have to help him, always pressing the right button at the right time.
Nothing complicated.
Surprisingly, though, there are far fewer landscapes in the game than you’d expect (specifically there are only three).
But the end result is positive, because this element does not become annoying and, in the context already mentioned, is one of the elements that make the game more interesting.
The driving model follows in the footsteps of previous episodes.
That means that today it is no longer a big deal, but it cannot be said to be bad.
If you are looking for a realistic simulation, you can look elsewhere.
But a race conceived with enough action is quite suitable for this style of driving, although we can find something better among the games of the competition.
So far, all in order.
But problems arise after a certain time.
Unlike the correct driving models, it is no longer the same with collisions.
Games of this type can not be expected to recreate deformations and complicated collisions, but in fact before a hit against any object, you can not predict how your car will react, with which everything is not in order.
It is typical that, when making a very tight overtaking or circulating the car with normal traffic, there are only slight frictions, but in other almost identical situations, your car ends up making uncontrolled pirouettes.
Or even completely destroyed.
Thanks to the reset system, no big problems arise, but it can put you in a bad mood.
Resets are scheduled in such a way that when you crash or get off the track, the game returns you to the last rescue point on the track.
However, in each race only five resets are available.
If you consume them all, you have to restart the race from the beginning.
So it is nothing more than a help in case something goes wrong, but it is not very reliable.
Sometimes, even the reset does not help, it only helps to learn the given stage by memory.
A big disadvantage of the game is that the same facts are repeated in different places.
In some curves, for example, you have to enter in a specific way; otherwise, they are impossible to take.
Other times you find yourself somewhere "civilian" vehicles always with the same configuration, even if you are the first, fifth or arrive five minutes before or after.
This makes it rabid especially in situations, when you see that two cars that go to meet in opposite directions, your opponent advances without problems, but when you arrive, you must turn or brake.
It doesn’t matter when you arrive, because it’s programmed because the “surprise” will always happen right under your noses.
Opponents also have an advantage.
Throughout the game you will reach places where, regardless of the moment, you will always be advanced by the same opponent in the same place.
In addition, this happens at the end of the game, on a long bridge, which is even more shocking.
Your opponent must arrive before you, whatever the cost.
When it goes in front of you, it makes it difficult for you to see the cars coming from the front, so at first you can muck up the car.
You can understand the idea of creating a game with maximum doses of suspense and adrenaline, but the execution is so apparent that it will surely disappoint you right away.
And it's a shame, because although the model of the trip is simple, the game is fun and action, so it is often not possible to follow in detail what happens or where.
And it really doesn’t matter, whether the merit takes the idea with fifty exclusive tracks or qualifying in the race so it doesn’t fit boredom, or anything else.
An unusual idea is changing cars during races.
You have to be attentive to the gas pumps next to the road, because just there you have to change cars, although in the vast majority of cases you will be enough what you have.
Cars are divided into three categories.
Sports cars are suitable for urban areas, strong American cars for straight highways and exotic supercars for technical driving, for example, on curved mountain roads.
In addition main narrative thread also appears a thread of parallel challenges, that is, there are races in specific places that you will know by the stories.
Here you will get not only medals, but also experience points for your profile, which serves both for challenges and stories.
Upon reaching the top level, the driver is opened several possibilities, starting with the car and ending with funds for the profile.
At the same time, there is an online Autolog feature, which compares your results with those of other players and provides other community features.
One of the most difficult elements to understand is how the last race in history is made.
With the car you get to the subway tunnel (pass), where you start to run in the dark on the tracks (pass).
The speedometer marks you between 150 and 200 km / h (pass) and, suddenly, from behind you arrives the convoy of the metro and takes you ahead without more.
In the newsroom we will surely have a discussion about this for several days, about whether during the programming of the game none thought even a little or if the authors really take us for a bunch of fools.
The technical part of the game is nothing extraordinary, but at least the general visual effects result in most cases pleasant, sometimes even superb.
Well, it is a pity that, in the most tense moments, the image quality is reduced and, sometimes, in a serious way.
This especially affects accidents where many participants are involved, when continuous image quality is no longer valid.
The audio is fine and the soundtrack is a matter of taste.
In order to please most of the youth group, the soundtrack belongs to the category "each of his father and mother", but it can be assumed that no one would buy the game just for its music.
Need for Speed: The Run is the first game in the Need for Speed series.
If the game avoided absolutely silly mistakes, we would have trouble claiming that The Run is the best NFS game of the last few years.
It feels like the game is not over.
The fun is guaranteed, but be prepared because mistakes will hit you in the eyes with the strength of an airport reflector.
The choirs of the Carolina University will participate in the concert "Students of Velvet".
The joint celebration of International Student Day and the anniversary of the Velvet Revolution as a musical experience will take place for the third time at the Festa Academica festival.
During it, twenty choirs from secondary and university centers will be presented.
The festival revolves around two concerts on November 17.
"Carolina University has a high turnout at the festival."
Among the current choirs are the choir of the Faculty of Pedagogy and the Faculty of Humanities, in the festival committee is the rector Václav Hampl, "said the head of the organization, Jakub <0xC4><0x8C>aloun.
